<h3><span id="Soci.C3.A9t.C3.A9s_savantes"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Sociétés_savantes">Sociétés savantes</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Paul_Krugman&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=18" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Sociétés savantes">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Paul_Krugman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Modifier la section : Sociétés savantes">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li>1986&#160;: Membre de la <a href="/wiki/Soci%C3%A9t%C3%A9_d%27%C3%A9conom%C3%A9trie" title="Société d&#39;économétrie">Société d'économétrie</a><sup id="cite_ref-68" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-68"><span class="cite_crochet">[</span>68<span class="cite_crochet">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>1992&#160;: Membre de l'<a href="/wiki/Acad%C3%A9mie_am%C3%A9ricaine_des_arts_et_des_sciences" title="Académie américaine des arts et des sciences">Académie américaine des arts et des sciences</a><sup id="cite_ref-69" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-69"><span class="cite_crochet">[</span>69<span class="cite_crochet">]</span></a></sup></li></ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Doctorats_honoris_causa">Doctorats honoris causa</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Paul_Krugman&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=19" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Doctorats honoris causa">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Paul_Krugman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Modifier la section : Doctorats honoris causa">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>Il a obtenu plusieurs <a href="/wiki/Doctorat_honoris_causa" title="Doctorat honoris causa">doctorats <i>honoris causa</i></a>&#160;:
